  "body": "It is critical that if you list a package in `tsconfig.json`, then you also list it in `tsconfig.build.json`. This is easy to get wrong especially when creating a new package. The first is important because you won't see type errors in your package otherwise; the second is important because you won't be able to publish your package otherwise.\r\n\r\nWe can write a script to check for this for now. In the future when we convert Yarn constraints to JavaScript, we can convert this to a Yarn constraint.",
